This is a dev extension for %1$s (%2$s), automatically added by the LeakCanary library.

LeakCanary is a memory leak detection library for Android, created and open sourced by Pierre-Yves Ricau at Square.

You can learn more about memory leaks at https://squ.re/leaks.

We welcome contributions from the community - please do not hesitate to report an issue or open a pull request!

FastAdapter, the bullet proof, fast and easy to use adapter library, which minimizes developing time to a fraction...
This library allows you to include vector icons everywhere in your project. No limits are given. Scale with no limit, use any Color at any time, provide a contour, and many additional customizations

AboutLibraries is a library to offer you all the information you need of your libraries!

Most modern apps feature a "Used Library"-section, which requires information about those respective libs. As it gets annoying to always copy those strings to your app, I have developed this small helper library to provide the required information.
ActionBar-PullToRefresh provides an easy way to add a modern version of the pull-to-refresh interaction to your application.
ActionBarSherlock is an standalone library designed to facilitate the use of the action bar design pattern across all versions of Android through a single API.
ActiveAndroid is an active record style ORM (object relational mapper).
Standalone Android widget for picking a single date from a calendar view.
Paging indicator widgets that are compatible with the ViewPager from the Android Support Library to improve discoverability of content.
This library adds support for the Action Bar user interface design pattern. This library includes support for material design user interface implementations.
Field and method binding for Android views which uses annotation processing to generate boilerplate code for you.
Custom view for circular images in Android while maintaining the best draw performance
Yet another implementation of Floating Action Button for Android with lots of features.
The Crashlytics Kit for Android provides simple APIs for reporting crashes.
Crouton is a class that can be used by Android developers that feel the need for an alternative to the Context insensitive Toast.
A fast dependency injector for Android and Java.
A fast dependency injector for Android and Java.

A custom view that displays an error image, a title, and a subtitle given an HTTP status code. It can be used for various other purposes like displaying other kinds of errors, or just messages with images.
EventBus is an Android optimized publish/subscribe event bus.
FButton is a custom Button of Android with Flat UI concept. FButton\'s design get inspiration from designmono. This library is very small and highly customizable.
Integrate Android apps with Facebook Platform.
Android Google+ like floating action button which reacts on the list view scrolling events. Becomes visible when the list view is scrolled up and invisible when scrolled down.

With Google Play services, your app can take advantage of the latest, Google-powered features such as Maps, Google+, and more, with automatic platform updates distributed as an APK through the Google Play store.

This library is an open-source set of graph types that are easy to add to your app, and in addition, look gorgeous. Themed in the much-loved Holo style of Android, the graphing library should fit in with any of your modern, standards-compliant apps.

JCIFS is an Open Source client library that implements the CIFS/SMB networking protocol in 100% Java. CIFS is the standard file sharing protocol on the Microsoft Windows platform (e.g. Map Network Drive …). This client is used extensively in production on large Intranets.
Tools and Libraries for the Advancement of Sciences.
A simple Android class for encrypting & decrypting strings, aiming to avoid the classic mistakes that most such classes suffer from.
jsoup is a Java library for working with real-world HTML. It provides a very convenient API for extracting and manipulating data, using the best of DOM, CSS, and jquery-like methods.
A memory leak detection library for Android and Java.
Screaming fast JSON parsing and serialization library for Android.
An android custom view that displays a circle with a colored arc given a mark.
MaterialRangeBar is a fork of https://github.com/edmodo/range-bar that adds some basic material styling, as well as start and end values, values as floats and some other things.
A material style progress wheel compatible with 2.3.
Extremely light way to execute code in the background on Android. Alternative to AsyncTask.
Android library for using the Honeycomb (Android 3.0) animation API on all versions of the platform back to 1.0!
An HTTP and SPDY client for Android and Java applications
Otto is an enhanced event bus with emphasis on Android support.
Interactive paging indicator widget, compatible with the ViewPager from the Android Support Library.
Paper is a fast NoSQL data storage for Android that lets you save/restore Java objects by using efficient Kryo serialization and handling data structure changes automatically.
A Powerful image downloading and caching library for Android.
Process Phoenix facilitates restarting your application process.
QuickReturn is a library which showcases the QuickReturn UI Pattern. The QuickReturn UI Pattern reveals or hides a header or footer as content is scrolled up or down.
A powerful Recyclerview wrapper for working with Realm as your datastore.
A simple and powerful EditText and RecyclerView UI component. It\'s build on top of RealmRecyclerView and RealmBasedRecyclerViewAdapter.
Realm is a mobile database: a replacement for SQLite & ORMs
The easiest way to create adapters! You can add a lot of different layouts and models. This library avoid all the boilerplates needed to create a list for your application.
A type-safe REST client for Android and Java.
RxJava binding APIs for Android\'s UI widgets.

The ShowcaseView library is designed to highlight and showcase specific parts of apps to the user with a distinctive and attractive overlay. This library is great for pointing out points of interest for users, gestures, or obscure but useful items.
This library includes support for application components, user interface features, accessibility, data handling, network connectivity, and programming utilities.
A logger with a small, extensible API which provides utility on top of Android\'s normal Log class.
Free (do whatever you want) high-resolution photos.
Flexible charting library with nice motion capabilities.
Library to implement the Bottom Navigation component from Material Design guidelines (minSdkVersion=14).
Alexei is a type-face Image Processor that allows developers to easily perform calculations over images.

This light-weight library provides images with letter/text like the Gmail app. It extends the Drawable class thus can be used with existing/custom/network ImageView classes. Also included is a fluent interface for creating drawables and a customizable ColorGenerator.
DialogFragments modeled after the 4.2 Alarm Clock TimePicker to improve UX for picking time, date, and numbers.

Iconify allows you to include any of the 361 FontAwesome icons by Dave Gandy in your texts, your ActionBar, and even in your EditTexts. Icons are infinitely scalable, and customizable with shadows and everything you can do on texts.
Backport of material dialogs with easy-to-use API based on DialogFragment. This library makes styling and using dialogs a piece of cake.
This RecyclerView extension library provides Google\'s Inbox app like swiping, Play Music app like drag-and-drop sorting and expandable item features. Works on API level 9 or later.
Yet another library for drawing Material Design promoted actions
Views and Drawable for displaying animated GIFs on Android
Image Cropping Library for Android, optimized for Camera / Gallery.
Android library to handle jobs in the background.
This open-source library contains classes that are useful for a wide range of applications using the Google Maps Android API.
Google Maps Android API utility library
The Easter Egg in the Android Settings App in Android Marshmallow, when you click multiple times on the version number. NOW CUSTOMIZABLE!
Provides a set of custom shaped android imageview components, and a framework to define more shapes. Implements both shader and bitmap mask based image views.
Insanely easy way to create clickable links within a TextView.
Easily upload files in the background with automatic Android Notification Center progress indication.

AndroidAnnotations is an Open Source framework that speeds up Android development. It takes care of the plumbing, and lets you concentrate on what\'s really important. By simplifying your code, it facilitates its maintenance.

AsyncService is born from an article I wrote a few weeks ago, which gave me a lot of feedbacks and interesting comments. AsyncService manages threading and caching transparently in your Android app. It is an alternative to AsyncTasks, Loaders, or more advanced libs like RxJava, Robospice, Groundy,… but AsyncService focuses on keeping your code short and simple!
CountryPicker is a simple fragment that can be embedded or shown as dialog. See the example to see more detail.
Extended linear layout that wrap its content when there is no place in the current line.
An Android Holo themed colorpicker designed by Marie Schweiz.
This is a simple, straight-forward implementation of the Android v3 In-app billing API. It supports: In-App Product Purchases (both non-consumable and consumable) and Subscriptions.
Material intro screen is inspired by Material Intro and developed with love from scratch.
Colorful progress bar with round corner on progress which you can customized a color and corner radius. A library has two type of progress bar.
Android Sliding Up Panel provides a simple way to add a draggable sliding up panel (popularized by Google Music, Google Maps and Rdio) to your Android application
Wrapper of StrictMode API that can be safely called on any version of Android.

UIL aims to provide a powerful, flexible and highly customizable instrument for image loading, caching and displaying. It provides a lot of configuration options and good control over the image loading and caching process.
A beautiful view to create a minimalistic hover effect over an ImageView
Anko is a library which makes Android application development faster and easier. It makes your code clean and easy to read, and lets you forget about rough edges of Android SDK for Java.

Apache MINA is a network application framework which helps users develop high performance and high scalability network applications easily. It provides an abstract event-driven asynchronous API over various transports such as TCP/IP and UDP/IP via Java NIO.
Android client SDK for communicating with OAuth 2.0 and OpenID Connect providers.
This library adds support for the Action Bar user interface design pattern.
AppIntro is an Android Library that helps you make a cool intro for your app, like the ones in Google apps.
Assent is designed to make Marshmallow\'s runtime permissions easier to use. Have the flexibility of request permissions and receiving results through callback interfaces.
Avatar ImageView with user\'s name first letter Drawable placeholder.
Android component which presents a dismissible view from the bottom of the screen.

Bridge is a simple but powerful HTTP networking library for Android. It features a Fluent chainable API, powered by Java/Android\'s URLConnection classes for maximum compatibility and speed.
Caldroid is a fragment that display calendar with dates in a month. Caldroid can be used as embedded fragment, or as dialog fragment. User can also swipe left/right to navigate to different months.
Custom fonts in Android the easy way…
Card Library provides an easy way to display a UI Card using the Official Google CardView in your Android app
Google’s Now popular Cards UI has everyone fascinated. This library aims to mimick this widget.
A lightweight viewpager indicator like in nexus 5 launcher
CloudRail is an API integration solution which abstracts multiple APIs from different providers into a single and universal interface.

This repository provides a simple collection of Color Picker.
• Color Picker from Stock Calendar
• Color Picker from Dashclock
The Apache Commons Compress library defines an API for working with ar, cpio, Unix dump, tar, zip, gzip, XZ, Pack200, bzip2, 7z, arj, lzma, snappy, DEFLATE, lz4, Brotli and Z files.
Commons CSV reads and writes files in variations of the Comma Separated Value (CSV) format.
Commons IO is a library of utilities to assist with developing IO functionality.
The standard Java libraries fail to provide enough methods for manipulation of its core classes. Apache Commons Lang provides these extra methods
Concurrent Radix and Suffix Trees for Java
The ConstraintLayout package allows you to create large and complex layouts with a flat view hierarchy
You can easily add awesome animated context menu to your app.
This library allows launching a custom activity when the app crashes, instead of showing the hated "Unfortunately, X has stopped" dialog.

A robust, powerful, and very simple ORM android database library with annotation processing.

The library is built on speed, performance, and approachability. It not only eliminates most boiler-plate code for dealing with databases, but also provides a powerful and simple API to manage interactions. Let DBFlow make SQL code flow like a steady stream so you can focus on writing amazing apps.

This library enables your Java application to handle property lists of various formats.

Property lists are files used to store user settings and serialized objects. They originate from the NeXSTEP programming environment and are now a basic part of the Cocoa framework (OS X and iOS) as well as the GNUstep framework.

The Design package provides APIs to support adding material design components and patterns to your apps. The Design Support library adds support for various material design components and patterns for app developers to build upon, such as navigation drawers, floating action buttons (FAB), snackbars, and tabs.
DiscreteSeekbar is my poor attempt to develop an android implementation of the Discrete Slider component from the Google Material Design Guidelines
Set of light and non-invasive extensions for Android RecyclerView widget. Does not use custom RecyclerView or LayoutManager. With this extensions you can create RecyclerView with following features:
Earl parses both Atom and RSS 1.0 and 2.0
A small library containing a wrapper/helper for the shared preferences of Android. With this library you can initialize the shared preference inside the onCreate of the Application class of your app.

Easy Android Animations is an animation library that aims to make android animations easier, with 50+ builtin animations, it allows you to introduce many complex animation effects in your application with one or two lines of code.
Encryption is a simple way to create encrypted strings to Android project.
Epoxy is an Android library for building complex screens in a RecyclerView.

ExoMedia is a media playback library with similar APIs to the Android MediaPlayer and VideoView that uses the ExoPlayer as a backing when possible, otherwise the default Android MediaPlayer and VideoView are used.

ExoPlayer is an application level media player for Android. It provides an alternative to Android’s MediaPlayer API for playing audio and video both locally and over the Internet. ExoPlayer supports features not currently supported by Android’s MediaPlayer API, including DASH and SmoothStreaming adaptive playbacks. Unlike the MediaPlayer API, ExoPlayer is easy to customize and extend, and can be updated through Play Store application updates.
It generates realistic fake data — like names, emails, dates, countries — for a variety of scenarios, including automated testing and database population.
FlexboxLayout is a library project which brings the similar capabilities of CSS Flexible Box Layout Module to Android.
A search view that implements a floating search bar also known as persistent search
Single Sign-on Library for Android applications to use Foursquare app for authorization.

The Apache FtpServer is a 100% pure Java FTP server. It\'s designed to be a complete and portable FTP server engine solution based on currently available open protocols. FtpServer can be run standalone as a Windows service or Unix/Linux daemon, or embedded into a Java application. We also provide support for integration within Spring applications and provide our releases as OSGi bundles.

Glide is a fast and efficient open source media management and image loading framework for Android that wraps media decoding, memory and disk caching, and resource pooling into a simple and easy to use interface.

A gradle plugin for getting java lambda support in java 6, 7 and android
greenDAO is a light and fast ORM solution for Android that maps objects to SQLite databases.
Gson is a Java library that can be used to convert Java Objects into their JSON representation.
A set of GSON serialiser/deserialisers for dealing with Joda Time entities.

The Guava project contains several of Google\'s core libraries that we rely on in our Java-based projects: collections, caching, primitives support, concurrency libraries, common annotations, string processing, I/O, and so forth.
Secure, simple key-value storage for android
Charting library for Android compatible with API 8+(Android 2.2).
Service for mobile crash analytics and app distribution
A simple library that allows you to select images from the device library or directly from the camera
A set of annotations used for code inspection support and code documentation.
Android Asynchronous Networking and Image Loading Library

Inspired by the quality and variety of XML tooling available for the Java platform (StAX, JAXB, etc.), the Jackson is a multi-purpose Java library for processing JSON data format. Jackson aims to be the best possible combination of fast, correct, lightweight, and ergonomic for developers.
Arthur van Hoff, Rick Blair, Kai Kreuzer
This is an implemenation of multi-cast DNS in Java. It supports service discovery and service registration. It is fully interoperable with Apple\'s Bonjour.
Joda-Time is a date and time library that vastly improves on the JDK.
Plain java unrar util (former sf project).
Celebrate more with this lightweight confetti particle system.

Butter Knife-esque view binding for Kotlin.
A small library replicating the new dialogs in android L.

Google\'s common Java, C++ and Javascript library for parsing, formatting, storing and validating international phone numbers. The Java version is optimized for running on smartphones, and is used by the Android framework since 4.0 (Ice Cream Sandwich)

The goal is to demonstrate techniques you may want to reuse in your root app that work around common problems, in as little code as possible. Advanced techniques like for example maintaining a background su session and using that session when needed are not covered by this article, for the sake of keeping it simple. The library does however include the Shell.Interactive class to make that possible..
A lightweight, good expandable Android library used for displaying different pages like loading, error, empty, timeout or even your custom page when you load data.
A Java implementation of the Magister 6 API for desktop and Android.
Material Design tap target for Android.
Makes it easy to create a beautiful about screen for your app.
As the name describes, this is an Android library that you can use to show new messages badge and new features badge.
Default colors and dimens per Material Design guidelines and Android Design guidelines inside one library.
A beautiful, easy-to-use, and customizable dialogs API, enabling you to use Material designed dialogs down to API 8
A Kotlin DSL wrapper around the mikepenz/MaterialDrawer library.
MaterialEditText, the EditText in Material Design, with more features that Google Material Design Spec has introduced.

android-material-icons allows you to include any of the Material Design 1.0.1 icons by Google packed by Sergey Kupletsky in your texts, your ActionBar, and even in your EditTexts. Icons are infinitely scalable, and customizable with shadows and everything you can do on texts.
The library provides two wrappers of MaterialMenuDrawable that eases implementation into the ActionBar, NavigationDrawer slide interaction or into any other custom layout.
Material Design ProgressBar with consistent appearance on Android 4.0+.
Material Design RatingBar with better appearance, compatible with Android 3.0+.
Mixpanel is the most advanced analytics platform for mobile & web.
Most popular Mocking framework for unit tests written in Java
A Model-View-Presenter and Model-View-Intent library for Android apps.
Moshi is a modern JSON library for Android and Java. It makes it easy to parse JSON into Java objects.

MPAndroidChart is a powerful and easy to use chart library for Android, supporting line-, bar-, scatter-, candlestick-, bubble-, pie- and radarcharts (spider web), as well as scaling, dragging (panning), selecting and animations.
MultiDex patches the application context class loader in order to load classes from more than one dex file.
Narrate is a beautiful and functional open source journal for Android
Android library to observe scroll events on scrollable views.
Okio is a new library that complements java.io and java.nio to make it much easier to access, store, and process your data.
Compile-time active record ORM for Android.
Parallax ListView and ScrollView for Android
The Android SDK provides a flexible and easy to integrate payment solution for your Android applications.
PermissionsDispatcher provides a simple annotation-based API to handle runtime permissions in Android Marshmallow
Implementation of ImageView for Android that supports zooming, by various touch gestures.
A Job Queue specifically written for Android to easily schedule jobs (tasks) that run in the background, improving UX and application stability.

The LG QCircle design template library provides the layout designs and basic UI elements through API, enabling developers to save time designing and using repetitive tasks. The LG QCircle design template library provides various circle layouts and receives QuickCircle broadcast intents, adjusts layout position, and handles back button operation.
LG QSlide is the feature on LG smartphones to provide an application with multi-tasking using floating window and quick execution using Notification bar.
ReactiveNetwork is an Android library listening network connection state and Internet connectivity with RxJava Observables.
Rebound is a java library that models spring dynamics. Rebound spring models can be used to create animations that feel natural by introducing real world physics to your application.

The recyclerview library adds the RecyclerView class. This class provides support for the RecyclerView widget, a view for efficiently displaying large data sets by providing a limited window of data items.
RecyclerView Animators is an Android library that allows developers to easily create RecyclerView with animations.
Backport of Java 8\'s lambda expressions to Java 7, 6 and 5
Robolectric is the industry-standard unit testing framework for Android. With Robolectric, your tests run in a simulated Android environment inside a JVM, without the overhead of an emulator.
Android Roboto Calendar View provides an easy and customizable calendar view with native support for the Roboto fonts, includes the brand new Roboto Slab fonts.

Android specific bindings for RxJava.

This module adds the minimum classes to RxJava that make writing reactive components in Android applications easy and hassle-free. More specifically, it provides a Scheduler that schedules on the main UI thread or any given Handler.

RxJava is a Java VM implementation of Reactive Extensions: a library for composing asynchronous and event-based programs by using observable sequences.

It extends the observer pattern to support sequences of data/events and adds operators that allow you to compose sequences together declaratively while abstracting away concerns about things like low-level threading, synchronization, thread-safety and concurrent data structures.
RxKotlin is a lightweight library that adds convenient extension functions to RxJava.
The utilities provided here allow for automatic completion of sequences based on Activity or Fragment lifecycle events.
Side menu with some categories to choose.
A rating toggle for Android which switches between 3 rating levels: positive, neutral, and negative

The Simple Logging Facade for Java (SLF4J) serves as a simple facade or abstraction for various logging frameworks (e.g. java.util.logging, logback, log4j) allowing the end user to plug in the desired logging framework at deployment time.

html.body:
How to access shared Windows folder on Android (SMB)


Enable File Sharing on Windows

Open the Control Panel, click Choose HomeGroup and Sharing options under Network and Internet, and click "Change Advanced Sharing Settings," enable the "File and Printer Sharing" feature.


Additional File Sharing settings

You may also want to configure the other advanced sharing settings here. 
 For example, you could enable access to your files without a password if you trust all the devices on your local network. Once file and printer sharing is enabled, you can open File Explorer or Windows Explorer, right-click a folder you want to share, and select Properties. 
 Click the Share button and make the folder available on the network.


Make sure both devices are on same Wifi

This feature makes files available on the local network, so your PC and mobile devices have to be on the same local network. You can\’t access a shared Windows folder over the Internet or when your smartphone is connected to its mobile data — it has to be connected to Wi-Fi.


Find IP Address

Open Command Prompt. Type 'ipconfig' and press Enter. Look for Default Gateway under your network adapter for your router's IP address. Look for \"IPv4 Address\" under the same adapter section to find your computer's IP address.


Enter details in SMB dialog box

html.body:
كيفية التوصل الى حافظة Windows المشتركة في Android (SMB) 
 

اتاحة مشاركة الملف على Windows 

قم بفتح لوحة التحكم ، واضغط اختيار HomeGroup واختيارات المشاركة تحت شبكة الاتصالات والانترنت ، واضغط "تغيير محددات المشاركة المتقدمة" ، واتاحة "ملف ومشاركة وحدة الطباعة" الخاصية المميزة. 
 

محددات مشاركة الملف الاضافية 

قد تريد أيضا توصيف محددات المشاركة المتقدمة الأخرى هنا. 
 على سبيل المثال ، يمكنك اتاحة امكانية الاتصال بالملفات الخاصة بك بدون كلمة سرية اذا كنت تثق بكل الأجهزة الموجودة على شبكة الاتصالات المحلية الخاصة بك. بمجرد اتاحة مشاركة الملف ووحدة الطباعة ، يمكنك فتح File Explorer أو Windows Explorer ، ثم اضغط بمفتاح الفأرة الأيمن على الحافظة التي تريد مشاركتها ، وحدد الاختيار خواص. 
 اضغط على الاختيار مشاركة واجعل الحافظة متاحة على شبكة الاتصال. 
 

تأكد من أن كلا من الأجهزة على نفس Wifi 

تقوم هذه الخاصية باتاحة الملفات الموجودة على شبكة الاتصالات المحلية ، ولذلك يجب أن يكون الحاسب الشخصي والأجهزة النقالة على نفس شبكة الاتصالات المحلية. لا يمكنك الاتصال بحافظة Windows المشتركة عبر شبكة الانترنت أو عند توصيل جهاز التليفون الذكي الخاص بك ببيانات الجهاز النقال الخاص به-يجب توصيله الى Wi-Fi. 
 

ايجاد عنوان IP 

فتح رسالة حث الأمر. أدخل 'ipconfig ' ثم اضغط Enter. ابحث عن Default Gateway تحت موفق شبكة الاتصالات الخاص بك لتوجيه مسار التوجيه الخاص بك ' عنوان IP. أنظر الى \ \"عنوان IPv4 \ \" تحت نفس قسم الموفق لايجاد IP الخاص بالحاسب الخاص بك عنوان.

string.html:
\\n
Cómo acceder a carpetes compartíes de Windows (SMB) n\'Android\\n \\n \\n
\\n Habilitar compartición de ficheros\\n
Abri\'l panel de control, primi Escoyer grupu del hogar y compartición so Rede ya internet, y primi Camudar axustes avanzaos de compartición. Habilita la carauterística de compartición ficheros ya imprentadores.\\n
Axustes de comparticion adicionales
Quiciabes quieras configurar equí los otros axustes de comparticion avanzada.\\nPor exemplu, podríes habilitar l\'accesu a los tos ficheros ensin una contraseña si t\'enfotes na to rede llocal. Una vegada s\'habilite la compartición de ficheros ya imprentadores, pues abrir l\'esplorador de ficheros o Windows Explorer, facer clic drechu na carpeta que quies compartir, y esbillar Propiedaes. \\nPrimi\'l boton Compartir y fai disponible la carpeta na rede.\\n
Asegúrate qu\'entrambos preseos tan na mesma Wi-Fi
\\n Esta carauterística pon disponibles los ficheros na rede llocal, pa qu\'asina\'l to PC y móvil tengan de tar na mesma rede llocal. Nun pue accedese a una carpeta compartida de Windows per internet — tien de tar coneutáu a la Wi-Fi.
\\n
Alcontrar direición IP\\n
Abri\'l Símbolu del sistema. Teclexa «ipconfig» primi Enter. Gueta la Pasera predeterminada sol to adautador de rede pa la direicion IP del router. Gueta «Direiciones IPv4» so la mesma estaya d\'adautadores p\'alcontrar la direicion IP del to ordenador.
\\n Introduz los detalles na caxa de diálogu SMB\\n
\\n \\n \\n

Уключыць агульны доступ да файлаў

Адкрыйце панэль кіравання, націсніце Выбраць хатнія групы і сумеснае выкарыстанне магчымасцяў у межах сеткі і Інтэрнэт, і націсніце кнопку Змяніць дадатковыя параметры агульнага доступу. Уключыць функцыі агульнага доступу да файлаў і друкарак.


Дадатковыя налады агульнага доступу да файлаў

Вы таксама можаце наладзіць іншыя дадатковыя параметры агульнага доступу тут.
 Напрыклад, вы можаце дазволіць доступ да файлаў без пароля, калі вы давяраеце ўсім прылады на вашай лакальнай сеткі.Адзін раз да файлаў і друкарак уключаны, вы можаце адкрыйце Праваднік або Праваднік Windows, націсніце правай кнопкай мышы тэчку, якой вы хочаце падзяліцца, і выберыце Уласцівасці. 
 Націсніце кнопку падзяліцца і зрабіць тэчку даступнай у сетцы.


Пераканайцеся, што абедзьве прылады падключаны на такі ж Wifi

Гэтая асаблівасць робіць файлы даступнымі ў лакальнай сеткі, так што ваш кампутар і мабільныя прылады павінны быць на той жа лакальнай сеткі. Вы маеце доступ да агульнай тэчцы Windows, праз Інтэрнэт або калі ваш смартфон падлучаны да сваёй мабільнай перадачы даных - гэта павінен быць падлучаны да Wi-Fi.


Find IP Адрас

Адкрыйце акно каманднага радка. Увядзіце 'IPCONFIG' і націсніце Enter. Паглядзіце на шлюз па змаўчанні пад сеткавай адаптар для IP-адрас маршрутызатара. Шукаць "IPv4 Address" у рамках таго ж адаптара раздзеле, каб знайсці IP вашага кампутара адрас.

html.body:
Jak můžu získat přístup ke sdílené složce Windows na platforme Android


Povolit sdílení souborů

Otevřete Ovládací panel, klikněte na tlačítko "Vybrat domácí skupinu a možnosti sdílení", klikněte na tlačítko "Změnit rozšířené nastavení sdílení" a prejděte na sdílení složek a tiskáren.


Rozšířené nastavení sdílení

Můžete nastavit i další pokročilé možnosti sdílení.
Například, můžete povolit přístup k souborům bez hesla pokud důvěřujete všem zařízením v síti. Jakmile je sdílení souborů a tiskáren zapnuto, otevřete Průzkumník Windows nebo jiného správce souborů, klikněte pravým tlačítkem myši na složku, ktorou chcete sdílet a vyberte možnost "Vlastnosti".
Kliknutím na tlačítko Sdílet bude složka dostupná v síti.


Uistěte se, že zařízení jsou ve stejné Wi-Fi síti

Vaše zařízení Windows a Android musí být na stejné síti. Například, že nemůžete mít přístup ke složce systému Windows na systém Android, když je vaše zařízení Android připojené na mobilní internet!


Vyhledávání IP adresy

Otevřete příkazový řádek. Zadejte 'ipconfig' a stiskněte Enter. Najděte "IPv4 adresu" adaptéru, kterým jsou Windows a Android zařízení připojené ke stejné síti.


Enter details in SMB dialog box

Wie freigegebenen Windows-Ordner Zugriff auf Android (Smb)


File-Sharing aktivieren 

Öffnen Sie die Systemsteuerung, klicken Sie auf Wählen Sie Heimnetzgruppe und Freigabeoptionen unter Netzwerk und Internet, und klicken Sie auf erweiterte Freigabeeinstellungen ändern. Aktivieren Sie die Datei- und Druckerfreigabe feature.


zusätzliche File-Sharing-Einstellungen 

kann auch die andere erweiterte Freigabe Einstellungen hier. 
 z. B. konfigurieren möchten, könnten Sie Zugriff auf Ihre Dateien ohne Passwort aktivieren, vertraust du alle Geräte in Ihrem lokalen Netzwerk. Wenn Datei- und Druckerfreigabe aktiviert ist, können Sie Datei-Explorer oder Windows Explorer zu öffnen, rechtsklicken Sie einen Ordner, den Sie freigeben möchten, und wählen Sie Eigenschaften. 
 Klicken Sie auf die Share-Taste und machen den Ordner finden Sie auf der network.


stellen sicher, dass beide Geräte sind auf dem gleichen Wifi 

dieses Feature macht Dateien im lokalen Netzwerk verfügbar, so dass Ihr PC und mobilen Geräten im gleichen lokalen Netzwerk sein. Sie können ' t Zugriff auf einen freigegebenen Windows-Ordner über das Internet oder wenn Ihr Smartphone mit seiner mobilen Daten verbunden ist – es hat mit Wi-Fi.

 verbunden sein
IP-Adresse suchen 

offenen Eingabeaufforderung. Geben Sie "Ipconfig" und drücken Sie die Eingabetaste. Suchen Sie nach Standard-Gateway unter Netzwerkadapter für die IP-Adresse Ihres Routers. Suchen Sie nach "IPv4 Address" unter den gleichen Adapter Abschnitt Ihres Computers IP-address.

Kiel atingi al Vindozan kunhavigitan dosierujon en Android-o (SMB)


Ebligi kunhavigon de dosiero

Malfermi el Kontrolpanelon, klaki "Choose homegroup and sharing options under Network and Internet", kaj klaki "Change advanced sharing settings". Ebligi la funkcion de dosieran kaj prresila kunhavigon.


Alia agordoj de dosiera kunhavigo

Vi eble volas agordi la alian specialajn kunhavigajn agordojn tie. 
 Ekzemple, vi povus ebligi atingi al viaj dosieroj sen pasvorto se vi konfidas ĉiojn aparatojn en via loka reto. Kiam dosiera kaj presila kunhavigo estas eblita, vi povas malfermi File Explorer aŭ Windows Explorer, dekstra-klaki dosierujon kiun vin volas kunhavigin, kaj elekti Properties. 
 Klaki la butonon "Share" kaj fari la dosierujon uzeblan en la reto.


Konfirmi aparatojn estas en sama Wifi reto

Ĉi tio funkcio faras dosierojn eblajn en la loka reto, do via PC-oj kaj poŝaparatoj devas esti en la sama loka reto. Vi ne povas atingi Vindozan kunhavigitan dosierujon en Interreto aŭ kiam via poŝkomputilo estas konektita to ĝia sendrata reto — ĝi devas esti konektita al Wi-Fi-o.


Serĉi IP-adreso

Malfermi "Command Prompt". Enigi 'ipconfig' kaj presi Eniga klavo. serĉi "Default Gateway" opcion malsur via retalira adaptilo por via enkursigila IP-adreso. Serĉi \"IPv4 Address\" malsur la sama adaptila sekcio por trovi vian komputilan IP adresojn.


Enigi detalojn en SMB-a dialogujo

html.body:
Como acceder a una carpeta compartida desde Windows (SMB)


Activar Compartición de Archivos

Abrir el Panel de Control, debajo de "Redes e Internet" seleccionar "Elegir grupo en el hogar y opciones de compartido" y seleccionar "Cambiar configuracion de uso compartido avanzado...". Activar las opciones de compartido de archivos e impresoras.


Opciones adicionales de comparticion de archivos

Puede que quiera configurar las otras opciones avanzadas de compartido aquí. 
 Por ejemplo, podria activar acceso a sus archivos sin contraseña si confia en todos los dispositivos en su red local. Una vez que el compatido de archivos e impresoras está activado puede abrir su navigador de archivos en su PC y hacer click derecho sobre la carpeta que desea compartir y seleccionar "Propiedades" y, luego, "Uso compartido" (pestaña), "Compartir...".


Ambos dispositivos deben estar en la misma red Wi-Fi

Esta característica hace que archivos esten disponibles en la red local, por lo que su PC o móvil deben estar conectados a la misma. No podrá acceder a sus archivos desde otras redes (incluyendo redes moviles).


Encontrar dirección IP

Abra una consola de comandos. Ingrese "ipconfig". 
 Debajo del adaptador de red, busque la sección "Puerta de enlace predeterminada" para obtener la IP de su enrutador (busque "Dirección IPv4" debajo de la sección con la IP de su PC).


Ingrese los detalles el dialogo de conexión SMB

html.body:
Cómo acceder a la carpeta compartida de Windows en android (smb)


Habilitar compartir archivos

Abra el Panel de control, haga clic en Elegir grupos domésticos y opciones de Internet, y haga clic en Cambiar la configuración avanzada de uso compartido. Habilitar el archivo y Función de compartir impresoras.


Configuración de archivos compartidos adicionales

También puedes configurar la configuración de uso compartido avanzada aquí.
 Por ejemplo, puedes habilitar el acceso a tus archivos sin una contraseña si confía en todos Los dispositivos de tu red local. Una vez que se habilite el intercambio de archivos e impresoras, puedes abrir el Explorador de archivos o el Explorador de Windows, hacer clic con el botón derecho en una carpeta que desees compartir y Seleccionar Propiedades.
 Hacer clic en el botón Compartir y hacer que la carpeta esté disponible en la red.


Asegúrate de que ambos dispositivos estén en la misma red Wifi

Esta característica hace que los archivos estén disponibles en la red local, por lo que su PC y dispositivos móviles tienen que estar en la misma red local. No puedes acceder a una carpeta de Windows compartida a través de Internet o cuando el teléfono esté conectado con datos móviles: Tiene que estar conectado al mismo Wi-Fi.


Buscar dirección IP

Abra el símbolo del sistema. Escriba 'ipconfig' y presione Enter. Buscar Default Gateway bajo tu adaptador de red para la dirección IP de tu enrutador. Busca \ "Dirección IPv4 \" en la misma sección del adaptador para encontrar la dirección IP de tu equipo dirección.


Introducir detalles en el cuadro de diálogo smb

Partekatutako Windows karpeta android-en atzitzeko (SMB)


Gaitu fitxategiak partekatzea

Ireki Kontrol-panela, klikatu Sarea eta Internet ataleko Aukeratu etxeko taldea eta partekatzeko aukerak eta klikatu Aldatu partekatzeko aukera aurreratuak. Gaitu fitxategiak eta inprimagailua partekatzeko ezaugarria.


Fitxategiak partekatzeko aukera gehigarriak

Partekatzeko ezarpen aurreratu gehiago konfigura ditzakezu. 
 Adibidez, zure sare lokaleko gailu guztietaz fidatzen bazara fitxategiak pasahitzik gabe atzitzea gaitu dezakezu. Fitxategiak eta inprimagailuak partekatzea gaituta badaude, fitxategi-arakatzailea edo Windows arakatzailea ireki dezakezu, eskuin klik egin partekatu nahi duzun karpetan eta hautatu Propietateak. 
 Klikatu Partekatu botoia eta karpetan sarean eskuragarri jarri.


Ziurtatu bi gailuak Wifi berean daudela

Ezaugarri honek fitxategiak sare lokalean eskuragarri jartzen ditu, horretarako zure PCak eta gailu mugikorrek sare lokal berean egon behar dute. Ezin duzu partekatutako Windows karpeta bat Internet-en zehar atzitu edo zure mugikorra datu mugikorretara konektatuta dagoenean — Wi-Fira konektatuta egon behar du.


Bilatu IP helbidea

Ireki komando-gonbita. Idatzi 'ipconfig' eta sakatu Enter. Ikusi zein den Default Gateway zure sare-moldagailuaren azpian zure bideratzailearen IP helbidea jakiteko. Begiratu \"IPv4 Address\" moldagailu beraren azpian zure ordenagailuaren IP helbidea jakiteko.

html.body:
How to access shared Windows folder on android (SMB)


Enable File Sharing

Open the Control Panel, click Choose homegroup and sharing options under Network and Internet, and click Change advanced sharing settings. Enable the file and printer sharing feature.


Additional File Sharing settings

You may also want to configure the other advanced sharing settings here. 
 For example, you could enable access to your files without a password if you trust all the devices on your local network.Once file and printer sharing is enabled, you can open File Explorer or Windows Explorer, right-click a folder you want to share, and select Properties. 
 Click the Share button and make the folder available on the network.


Make sure both devices are on same Wifi

This feature makes files available on the local network, so your PC and mobile devices have to be on the same local network. You can\’t access a shared Windows folder over the Internet or when your smartphone is connected to its mobile data — it has to be connected to Wi-Fi.


Find IP Address

Open Command Prompt. Type 'ipconfig' and press Enter. Look for Default Gateway under your network adapter for your router's IP address. Look for \"IPv4 Address\" under the same adapter section to find your computer's IP address.


Enter details in SMB dialog box

string.html:
\\n
Comment accéder à un dossier partager de Windows sous Android (SMB)\\n \\n \\n
\\n Activation du partage de fichiers\\n
Ouvrer le Panneau de Configuration, cliquer sur Choisir les options de groupe résidentiel et de partage sous Réseau et Internet, et cliquer sur changer les options des partages avancées. Active l\'option de partage de fichiers et d\'imprimantes\\n
Options de partages de fichiers avancées
Vous pouvez aussi régler d\'autres paramètres de partages à cet endroit. Par exemple, vous pouvez autoriser l\'accès à vos fichiers sans mot de passe si vous vous trouvez dans un réseau de confiance (réseau domestique). Une fois que le partage de fichiers et d\'imprimantes est activé, vous pouvez ouvrir l\'Explorateur de fichiers, clique-droit sur un dossier à partager, et sélectionner Propriétés.\\n Cliquer sur l\'onglet Partage et rendre le dossier accessible sur votre réseau.\\n
Assurez-vous que les deux appareils soient connectés au même réseau Wifi
\\n Cette fonction rend disponible vos fichiers sur un réseau local, donc votre PC et votre appareil mobile doit se trouver sur le même réseau local. Vous ne pouvez pas accéder à vos partages Windows à travers Internet où quand votre appareil mobile est connecté au réseau cellulaire - Il doit être connecté au Wifi.
\\n
Trouver votre adresse IP\\n
Ouvrez une invite de commande. Tapez \'ipconfig\' et appuyez sur Entrer. Regarder la valeur de Passerelle par défaut pour connaitre l\'IP de votre routeur. Regardez \"Adresse IPv4 \" pour connaitre l\'adresse IP de votre ordinateur.
\\n Entrer les détails dans le fenêtre de configuration de SMB\\n
\\n \\n \\n

html.body:
איך לגשת לתיקיית Windows משותפת דרךAndroid (SMB)


הפעלת שיתוף קבצים ב־Windows

עליך לפתוח את לוח הבקרה, ללחוץ על בחירת קבוצה ביתית ואפשרויות שיתוף תחת רשת ואינטרנט, וללחוץ על „שינוי הגדרות שיתוף מתקדמות”, להפעיל את התכונה „שיתוף קבצים ומדפסות”.


הגדרות שיתוף קבצים נוספות

אולי גם יעניין אותך להגדיר הגדרות שיתוף קבצים נוספות. 
 כמו למשל להפעיל גישה לקבצים שלך ללא ססמה אם כל המכשירים ברשת המקומית שלך מהימנים. לאחר ששיתוף קבצים ומדפסות פעיל, ניתן לפתוח סייר הקבצים או סייר Windows, ללחוץ עם המקש הימני על תיקייה שברצונך לשתף, לבחור במאפיינים. 
 ללחוץ על כפתור השיתוף ולאפשר את הגישה לתיקייה דרך הרשת..


יש לוודא ששני המכשירים באותה הרשת

תכונה זו מאפשרת לשתף קבצים דרך רשת מקומית, לכן על המחשב ועל הטלפון הנייד שלך להיות מחוברים לאותה רשת מקומית. אין לך אפשרות לגשת לתיקיית ה־Windows המשותפת דרך האינטרנט או כאשר הטלפון שלך מחובר לתקשורת נתונים סלולרית — יש לחבר אותו לרשת האלחוטית.


איתור כתובת ה־IP

יש לפתוח את מסוף הפקודות. להקליד ‚ipconfig’ ואז Enter. להסתכל על שער בררת המחדל תחת מתאם הרשת של כתובת ה־IP של הנתב שלך. יש לחפש כתובת \"IPv4\" תחת הסעיף של אותו המתאם כדי למצוא את כתובת ה־IP של המחשב שלך.


נא להכניס את הפרטים בתיבה של ה־SMB

יכול להיות שמדובר בהאזנה שמתרחשת כרגע (סוכן אמצע)! יכול גם להיות שמפתח המארח השתנה ממש כרגע. טביעת האצבע של המפתח הציבורי שנשלח מצד המארח המרוחק אינו תואם לזו שמאוחסנת ב־Amaze.

Hogyan érhető el a megosztott Windows mappa androidon (SMB)


Engedélyezze a fájlmegosztást

Nyissa meg a Vezérlőpultot, kattintson az Otthoni csoport és megosztás kiválasztása ikonra a Hálózat és Internet alatt, majd kattintson a Speciális megosztási beállítások módosítása hivatkozásra. Engedélyezze a fájl- és nyomtatómegosztás funkciót.


További fájlmegosztási beállítások

Itt további speciális megosztási beálítások konfigurálására nyílik lehetősége. 
 Például, engedélyezheti a fájlok jelszó nélküli elérését, ha megbízik a helyi hálózaton lévő összes eszközben. A fájl- és nyomtatómegosztás engedélyezése után megnyithatja a Fájlkezelőt vagy a Windows Intézőt, kattintson jobb gombbal a megosztani kívánt mappára, és válassza a Tulajdonságok lehetőséget. 
 Kattintson a Megosztás gombra, és tegye a mappát elérhetővé a hálózaton.


Győződjön meg arról, hogy mindkét eszköz ugyanazon a Wifi hálózaton van

Ez a funkció elérhetővé teszi a fájlokat a helyi hálózaton, így PC-je, illetve mobil készüléke ugyanazon a helyi hálózaton lesz. Nem férhet hozzá a megosztott Windows mappához interneten keresztül vagy okostelefonjáról mobil adatátviteli kapcsolat használatával — ehhez kapcsolódnia kell a Wi-Fi-hez.


IP-cím keresése

Nyissa meg a parancssort. Írja be az 'ipconfig' parancsot, majd nyomja le az Enter billentyűt. Keresse az alapértelmezett átjárót a hálózati adapter alatt routere IP-címével. Keresse az \"IPv4-cím\" bejegyzést ugyanabban a csatoló részben számítógépe IP-címének megtalálásához.

Bagaimana cara mengakses folder berbagi Windows di android (SMB)


Aktifkan Berbagi Berkas

Buka Panel Kontrol, klik Pilih grup rumah dan opsi berbagi di bawah Jaringan dan Internet, and klik Ubah pengaturan berbagi lanjutan. Aktifkan fitur berbagi berkas dan printer.


Pengaturan Berbagi Berkas Tambahan

Anda mungkin juga ingin mengubah pengaturan berbagi lanjutan di sini. 
 Contohnya, Anda bisa mengaktifkan akses ke berkas Anda tanpa sandi jika Anda mempercayai semua perangkat di jaringan lokal Anda. Setelah opsi berbagi berkas dan printer diaktifkan, Anda bisa membuka File Explorer atau Windows Explorer, klik kanan folder yang ingin Anda bagikan, dan pilih Properti. 
 Pilih tab Berbagi lalu klik tombol Berbagi dan buat folder tersedia di Jaringan.


Pastikan kedua perangkat Anda berada di jaringan Wi-Fi yang sama

Fitur ini membuat berkas tersedia pada jaringan local, jadi perangkat PC dan seluler Anda harus berada di jaringan lokal yang sama. Anda tidak bisa mengakses folder berbagi Windows dari Internet atau ketika telepon seluler Anda tersambung ke jaringan 3G/4G — perangkat harus tersambung ke jaringan Wi-Fi yang sama.


Temukan Alamat IP

Buka Command Prompt. Ketik 'ipconfig' dan tekan Enter. Cari Default Gateway di bawah adapter jaringan untuk router Anda. Cari \"IPv4 Address\" di bagian yang sama untuk menemukan alamat IP komputer Anda.


Masukkan detailnya di kotak dialog SMB

Bagaimana cara mengakses folder berbagi Windows di android (SMB)


Aktifkan Berbagi Berkas

Buka Panel Kontrol, klik Pilih grup rumah dan opsi berbagi di bawah Jaringan dan Internet, and klik Ubah pengaturan berbagi lanjutan. Aktifkan fitur berbagi berkas dan printer.


Pengaturan Berbagi Berkas Tambahan

Anda mungkin juga ingin mengubah pengaturan berbagi lanjutan di sini. 
 Contohnya, Anda bisa mengaktifkan akses ke berkas Anda tanpa sandi jika Anda mempercayai semua perangkat di jaringan lokal Anda. Setelah opsi berbagi berkas dan printer diaktifkan, Anda bisa membuka File Explorer atau Windows Explorer, klik kanan folder yang ingin Anda bagikan, dan pilih Properti. 
 Pilih tab Berbagi lalu klik tombol Berbagi dan buat folder tersedia di Jaringan.


Pastikan kedua perangkat Anda berada di jaringan Wi-Fi yang sama

Fitur ini membuat berkas tersedia pada jaringan local, jadi perangkat PC dan seluler Anda harus berada di jaringan lokal yang sama. Anda tidak bisa mengakses folder berbagi Windows dari Internet atau ketika telepon seluler Anda tersambung ke jaringan 3G/4G — perangkat harus tersambung ke jaringan Wi-Fi yang sama.


Temukan Alamat IP

Buka Command Prompt. Ketik 'ipconfig' dan tekan Enter. Cari Default Gateway di bawah adapter jaringan untuk router Anda. Cari \"IPv4 Address\" di bagian yang sama untuk menemukan alamat IP komputer Anda.

html.body:
Hvernig hægt er að tengjast sameiginlegri Windows-möppu á Android (SMB)


Virkjaðu skráadeilingu á Windows

Opnaðu stjórnskjáinn (Control Panel), smelltu á 'Choose homegroup and sharing options' undir 'Network and Internet' og smelltu síðan á 'Change advanced sharing settings'. Virkjaðu deilimöguleikana fyrir skrár og prentun.


Viðbótarstillingar fyrir skráadeilingu

Þú gætir einnig viljað stilla hérna aðra ítarlegri valkosti deilingar. 
 Til dæmis getur þú virkjað aðgang að skránum þínum án lykilorðs EF þú treystir öllum tækjum á staðarnetinu þínu. Eftir að deiling skráa og prentunar hefur verið virkjuð, geturðu opnað File Explorer eða Windows Explorer skráastjóra, hægri-smellt á möppu sem þú vilt deila, og valið eiginleika hennar (Properties). 
 Smelltu á Deila/Share hnappinn og gerðu möppuna tiltæka á netkerfinu.


Gakktu úr skugga um að bæði tækin séu á sama Wi-Fi-netinu

Þessi eiginleiki gerir skrár tiltækar á staðarnetinu, þannig að tölvan þín og snjalltæki verða að vera á sama staðarneti. Þú getur ekki fengið aðgang að sameiginlegri Windows-möppu í gegnum Internetið eða þegar farsíminn er tengdur í gegnum símkerfið — hann verður að vera tendur í gegnum þráðlausa Wi-Fi-netið.


Finndu IP-vistfangið

Opnaðu Command Prompt skipanalínuforritið. Skrifaðu 'ipconfig' og ýttu á Enter. Leitaðu að 'Default Gateway' netkortsins fyrir IP-vistfang beinisins (router). Leitaðu að \"IPv4 Address\" undir hlutanum sem tilheyrir netkortinu til að sjá IP-vistfang tölvunnar.

Come accedere alla cartella condivisa di Windows (smb) android


Abilita condivisione File 

aprire il pannello di controllo, fare clic su Scegli Gruppo Home e opzioni in rete e Internet di condivisione e fare clic su Modifica impostazioni di condivisione avanzata. Abilitare la condivisione file e stampanti feature.


impostazioni di condivisione di File aggiuntivi 

è possibile anche configurare l'altro avanzate impostazioni condivisione qui. 
 ad esempio, è possibile abilitare l'accesso ai tuoi file senza una password se ti fidi di tutti i dispositivi sulla rete locale. Una volta che condivisione file e stampanti è attivata, si può aprire Esplora File o Esplora risorse di Windows, destro del mouse su una cartella che si desidera condividere e selezionare Proprietà. 
 clicca sul pulsante Condividi e rendere la cartella disponibile sulla network.


assicurarsi che entrambi i dispositivi siano sulla stessa Wifi 

questa caratteristica rende i file disponibili sulla rete locale, quindi il vostro PC e dispositivi mobili devono essere sulla stessa rete locale. Si can ' t accedere una cartella condivisa di Windows su Internet o quando lo smartphone è collegato ai suoi dati mobili — deve essere collegato a Wi-Fi.


Trovare IP indirizzo 

Open Command Prompt. Digitare "ipconfig" e premere INVIO. Guardare per Default Gateway sotto la scheda di rete per l'indirizzo IP del router. Cercare "IPv4 Address" sotto la stessa sezione di adattatore per trovare IP address.

html.body:
איך לגשת לתיקיית Windows משותפת דרךAndroid (SMB)


הפעלת שיתוף קבצים ב־Windows

עליך לפתוח את לוח הבקרה, ללחוץ על בחירת קבוצה ביתית ואפשרויות שיתוף תחת רשת ואינטרנט, וללחוץ על „שינוי הגדרות שיתוף מתקדמות”, להפעיל את התכונה „שיתוף קבצים ומדפסות”.


הגדרות שיתוף קבצים נוספות

אולי גם יעניין אותך להגדיר הגדרות שיתוף קבצים נוספות. 
 כמו למשל להפעיל גישה לקבצים שלך ללא ססמה אם כל המכשירים ברשת המקומית שלך מהימנים. לאחר ששיתוף קבצים ומדפסות פעיל, ניתן לפתוח סייר הקבצים או סייר Windows, ללחוץ עם המקש הימני על תיקייה שברצונך לשתף, לבחור במאפיינים. 
 ללחוץ על כפתור השיתוף ולאפשר את הגישה לתיקייה דרך הרשת..


יש לוודא ששני המכשירים באותה הרשת

תכונה זו מאפשרת לשתף קבצים דרך רשת מקומית, לכן על המחשב ועל הטלפון הנייד שלך להיות מחוברים לאותה רשת מקומית. אין לך אפשרות לגשת לתיקיית ה־Windows המשותפת דרך האינטרנט או כאשר הטלפון שלך מחובר לתקשורת נתונים סלולרית — יש לחבר אותו לרשת האלחוטית.


איתור כתובת ה־IP

יש לפתוח את מסוף הפקודות. להקליד ‚ipconfig’ ואז Enter. להסתכל על שער בררת המחדל תחת מתאם הרשת של כתובת ה־IP של הנתב שלך. יש לחפש כתובת \"IPv4\" תחת הסעיף של אותו המתאם כדי למצוא את כתובת ה־IP של המחשב שלך.


נא להכניס את הפרטים בתיבה של ה־SMB

html.body:
Android で共有の Windows フォルダーにアクセスする方法 (SMB)


Windows でファイル共有を有効にします

コントロールパネルを開き、ネットワークとインターネットの下のホームグループと共有オプションを選択をクリックし、 共有の詳細設定の変更をクリックします。 ファイルとプリンターの共有機能を有効にします。


追加のファイル共有設定

また、その他の詳細な共有設定はここにあります。 
 たとえば、ローカルネットワーク上のデバイスをすべての信頼する場合は、 パスワードなしでファイルへのアクセスを有効にすることができます。 ファイルとプリンタの共有が有効になっているときは、 ファイルエクスプローラーまたは Windows エクスプローラーを開き、共有するフォルダを右クリックし、 プロパティを選択します。
 共有ボタンをクリックして、ネットワーク上でフォルダーを利用可能にします。


両方のデバイスが同じ Wifi に接続されていることを確認します。 

この機能により、ローカルネットワーク上でファイルを利用できるようになります。そのため、PC とモバイルデバイスは、 同じローカルネットワーク上にいる必要があります。インターネットを介して、またはスマートフォンがモバイルデータに接続されているときは 共有 Windows フォルダーにアクセスできません — Wi-Fiに接続する必要があります。


IP アドレスの検索

コマンドプロンプトを開きます。 'ipconfig' と入力し、Enter キーを押します。 お使いのルーターの IP アドレス用のネットワークアダプターの下にあるデフォルトゲートウェイを探します。 同じアダプタセクションの下の "IPv4 アドレス" を探して、コンピュータの IP アドレスを確認します。


詳細を SMB ダイアログボックスに入力します

Jak uzyskać dostęp na Androidzie do folderu udostępnionego w Windows


Włącz "Udostępnianie plików"

Otwórz Panel sterowania, kliknij "Wybierz grupę domową" i opcje udostępniania przez Internet, a potem kliknij "Zmień zaawansowane opcje udostępniania. Włącz plik i uruchom funkcję udostępniania drukarki.


Dodatkowe ustawienia udostępnianych plików

Możesz tutaj skonfigurować również inne zaawansowane opcje udostępniania. 
 Na przykład możesz zezwolić na dostęp do twoich plików bez podawania hasła, jeżeli rozpoznajesz wszystkie urządzenia w sieci lokalnej. Gdy udostępnianie plików i drukarek jest włączone, otwórz Eksplorator plików lub Eksplorator Windows, kliknij prawym przyciskiem myszy na folder, który chcesz udostępnić, i wybierz "Właściwości". 
 Kliknij przycisk "Udostępnij", aby folder był dostępny w sieci.


Upewnij się, że oba urządzenia są w tej samej sieci Wi-Fi

Dzięki temu pliki staną się dostępne w sieci lokalnej; twój komputer i urządzenie mobilne muszą pracować w tej samej sieci lokalnej. Nie możesz uzyskać dostępu do folderu Windows udostępnionego przez Internet albo gdy twój smartfon korzysta z niego za pośrednictwem łączności mobilnej. Musisz być połączony przez Wi-Fi.


Znajdź adres IP

Otwórz okno Wiersza poleceń. Wpisz "ipconfig" i naciśnij Enter. Sprawdź domyślną bramkę zgodną z twoją kartą sieciową dla adresu IP rutera. Szukaj "Adres IPv4" w tej samej sekcji karty, aby znaleźć adres IP komputera.

html.body:
Como acessar a pasta compartilhada do Windows no android (smb)


Ativar compartilhamento de arquivos

Abra o Painel de Controle, clique em Escolher o grupo doméstico e as opções de compartilhamento em Rede e Internet e clique em Alterar configurações de compartilhamento avançadas. Ative o recurso de compartilhamento de arquivos e impressoras.


Configurações adicionais de compartilhamento de arquivos

Você também pode querer configurar as outras configurações de compartilhamento avançadas aqui. 
 Por exemplo, você pode habilitar o acesso aos seus arquivos sem uma senha se confiar em todos os dispositivos da sua rede local. Uma vez que o compartilhamento de arquivos e impressoras estiver ativado, abra o File Explorer ou Windows Explorer, clique com o botão direito do mouse na pasta que deseja compartilhar e selecione Propriedades. 
 Clique no botão Compartilhar e disponibilize a pasta na rede.


Certifique-se de que ambos os dispositivos estejam na mesma rede Wi-Fi

Esta funcionalidade torna os arquivos disponíveis na rede local, por isso o seu PC e os dispositivos móveis têm de estar na mesma rede local. Você não pode acessar uma pasta compartilhada do Windows pela Internet ou quando o smartphone estiver utilizando dados móveis - ele precisa estar conectado ao Wi-Fi.


Localizar endereço IP

Abra o Prompt de Comando. Digite 'ipconfig' e pressione Enter. Procure por Gateway Padrão em seu adaptador de rede para o endereço IP do seu roteador. Procure por \"Endereço IPv4\" na mesma seção do adaptador para encontrar o endereço IP do seu computador.

html.body:
Как получить доступ к общей папки Windows на Android


Включить общий доступ к файлам

Откройте панель управления, нажмите «Выбор домашней группы и параметров общего доступа», далее нажмите «Изменить дополнительные параметры общего доступа» и включите общий доступ к папкам и принтерам.


Дополнительные параметры общего доступа

Вы также можете настроить другие дополнительные параметры общего доступа здесь. 
Например, вы можете разрешить доступ к файлам без пароля, если Вы доверяете всем устройства в этой сети. После того, как общий доступ к файлам и принтерам включен, откройте Проводник Windows или другой файловый менеджер, щелкните правой кнопкой мыши по папке, которой Вы хотите поделиться, и нажмите «Свойства». 
После перейдите на вкладку «Доступ» и откройте общий доступ к папке. 


Убедитесь, что устройства находятся в одной сети

Ваши устройства Windows и Android должны находиться в одной локальной сети. Например, Вы не получите доступ к папке из Windows на Android, если на устройстве Android будет включён только мобильный интернет!


Поиск IP адреса

Откройте командную строку. Введите 'ipconfig' и нажмите Enter. Найдите "IPv4-адрес" адаптера, через который Windows и Android устройства подключены к одной сети.

Ako môžem získať prístup k zdieľanému priečinku Windows na platforme Android


Povoliť zdieľanie súborov

Otvorte Ovládací panel, kliknite na tlačidlo "Vybrať domácu skupinu a možnosti zdieľania", kliknite na tlačidlo "Zmeniť rozšírené nastavenie zdieľania" a prejdite na zdieľanie zložiek a tlačiarní.


Rozšírené nastavenia zdieľania

Môžete tam nastaviť aj ďalšie pokročilé možnosti zdieľania.
Napríklad, môžete povoliť prístup k súborom bez hesla, ak dôverujete všetkým zariadeniam v sieti. Akonáhle je zdieľanie súborov a tlačiarní zapnuté, otvorte Prieskumníka Windows alebo iného správcu súborov, kliknite pravým tlačidlom myši na priečinok, ktorý chcete zdieľať a vyberte možnosť "Vlastnosti".
Kliknutím na tlačidlo Zdieľať bude priečinok dostupný na sieti.


Uistite sa, že zariadenia sú v rovnakej Wi-Fi sieti

Vaše zariadenie Windows a Android musia byť na rovnakej sieti. Napríklad, že nemôžete mať prístup k priečinku systému Windows na systém Android, ak je vaše zariadenie Android pripojené na mobilný internet!


Vyhľadanie IP adresy

Otvorte príkazový riadok. Zadajte 'ipconfig' a stlačte Enter. Nájdite "IPv4 adresu" adaptéra, ktorým sú Windows a Android zariadenia pripojené k rovnakej sieti.

html.body:
Hur man får tillgång till delade Windowsmappar i Android (SMB)


Slå på Fildelning i Windows

Öppna kontrollpanelen, klicka på Välj Hem Grupp och Delningsalternativ under Nätverk och Internet, och klicka på "Ändra Avancerade Delningsalternativ," Slå på funktionen "Fil- och Skrivardelning".


Ytterligare Fildelningsalternativ

Det kan också vara så att du vill konfigurera andra avancerade delningsalternativ här. 
 T.ex så kan du slå på tillgång till dina filer utan lösenord om du litar på alla enheter på ditt lokala nätverk. När väl Fil- och Skrivardelning är påslagen, då kan du öppna Utforskaren, högerklicka på den mapp du vill dela och välja Egenskaper. 
 Klicka på Dela-knappen och gör mappen tillgänglig på nätverket.


Se till att båda enheterna är på samma Wi-Fi-nät

Den här funktionen gör filer tillgängliga på det lokala nätverket, så din PC och bärbara enheter måste vara anslutna till samma lokala nätverk. Du kan inte komma åt en delad Windowsmapp över Internet eller när din smartphone är ansluten via mobildata — den måste vara ansluten via Wi-Fi.


Hitta IP-adress

Öppna kommandotolken. Skriv 'ipconfig' och tryck Enter. Leta efter Default Gateway under din nätverks-adapter för din routers IP-adress. Leta efter \"IPv4 Address\" i samma stycke för att hitta din dators IP-adress.

இது முறைமை நிரல், இதை நீக்கினால் முறைமை நிலையற்றதாகிவிடும்.\\nதொடரவேண்டுமா?

Android'de paylaşılan Windows klasörüne nasıl erişilir (smb)


Dosya Paylaşımını Etkinleştirme

Denetim Masasını açın, Ağ ve İnternet'in altındaki ev grubu ve paylaşım seçeneklerini belirle'yi tıklayın ve Gelişmiş paylaşım ayarlarını değiştir'i tıklayın. Dosyayı ve yazıcı paylaşma özelliğini etkinleştirin.


Ek Dosya Paylaşımı ayarları

Diğer gelişmiş paylaşım ayarlarını burada da yapılandırmak isteyebilirsiniz.
 Örneğin, yerel ağınızdaki tüm aygıtlara güveniyorsanız, dosyalarınıza şifre olmadan erişimi etkinleştirebilirsiniz. Dosya ve yazıcı paylaşımı etkinleştirildiğinde, Dosya Gezgini'ni veya Windows Gezgini'ni açın, paylaşmak istediğiniz klasörü sağ tıklayın Ve Özellikler'i seçin.
 Paylaş düğmesini tıklayın ve klasörü ağ üzerinde kullanılabilir yapın.


Her iki cihazın aynı kablosuz ağa bağlı olduğundan emin olun

Bu özellik, dosyaları yerel ağda kullanılabilir hale getirir, bu nedenle bilgisayarınız ve mobil cihazlarınızın aynı yerel ağ üzerinde olması gerekir. Telefonunuzda mobil veri ile internete bağlı iseniz Internet üzerinden paylaşılan bir Windows klasörüne erişemezsiniz. Wi-Fi ile bağlanmış olmanız gerekmektedir.


IP Adresi Bulma

Komut İstemi'ni açın. 'Ipconfig' yazıp Enter tuşuna basın. Yönelticinizin IP adresi için Ağ Bağdaştırıcınızın Altındaki Varsayılan Ağ Geçidi'ne bakın. Bilgisayarınızın IP adresini bulmak için aynı bağdaştırıcı bölümünde \ "IPv4 Adresi \" bölümüne bakın.

Як отримати доступ до спільної папки вікна на андроїд (smb)


Увімкнути загальний доступ до файлів

Відкрийте панель управління, натисніть Вибрати домашні групи і спільне використання можливостей в межах мережі та Інтернет, і натисніть кнопку Змінити додаткові параметри спільного доступу. Включити функції загального доступу до файлів і принтерів.


Additional File Sharing settings

You may also want to configure the other advanced sharing settings here. 
 For example, you could enable access to your files without a password if you trust all the devices on your local network.Once file and printer sharing is enabled, you can open File Explorer or Windows Explorer, right-click a folder you want to share, and select Properties. 
 Click the Share button and make the folder available on the network.


Make sure both devices are on same Wifi

This feature makes files available on the local network, so your PC and mobile devices have to be on the same local network. You can\’t access a shared Windows folder over the Internet or when your smartphone is connected to its mobile data — it has to be connected to Wi-Fi.


Find IP Address

Open Command Prompt. Type 'ipconfig' and press Enter. Look for Default Gateway under your network adapter for your router's IP address. Look for "IPv4 Address" under the same adapter section to find your computer's IP address.

html.body:
如何在 Android 上访问 Window(smb) 共享文件夹？


启用文件共享功能

在 Windows 中打开控制面板，点击“网络和 Internet——选择家庭组和共享选项——更改高级共享设置——启用文件和打印机共享功能”。


其他文件共享设置

您还可以设置一些其他高级选项。
 如：如果您信任本地网络上的所有设备，则可以无需密码访问文件。具体做法是在 Windows 中启用文件和打印机共享功能后， 打开资源管理器，右键点击您想要共享的文件夹并选择“属性——共享”。

确保设备处于同一的局域网

此功能使文件在本地网络上可用，因此您的 PC 和移动设备必须处于同一个本地网络上。 当您的设备使用移动数据时，您无法通过 Internet 访问共享的 Windows 文件夹——您必须链接同一局域网。


查找 IP 地址

在 Windows 中打开命令提示符，输入 ipconfig 后按回车键。 网络适配器下的“默认网关”即是您路由器的 IP 地址。“IPv4 地址”即是您计算机的IP地址。


在 SMB 对话框中输入详细信息。

如何存取共用 Windows 資料夾上的 android (SMB)
 
 


 啟用檔案共用 

開啟控制台，點選選擇家用群組和共用選項下網路和網際網怒，並按一下更改進階共用設定。啟用檔案和印表機共用功能 

其他檔案共用設定
您可能還想配置其他例如進階共用設定這裡 
，您可以啟用存取您無需密碼的檔案，如果您相信在您的本地網路上的所有裝置。一旦啟用了檔案和印表機共用，則可以開啟檔案資源管理器或 Windows 檔案總管中，按右鍵您想要共用的資料夾並選擇屬性。
 按一下共用按鈕，使此資料夾可在 
 網路。
確保兩個裝置都在相同的 Wi-Fi

 此功能使檔可用在本地網路上，因此您的 PC 和行動裝置必須具有相同的本地網路上。您無法無法訪問共用的 Windows 資料夾透過網際網路或您的智慧手機連線至其行動數據時 — — 已連線至 Wi-Fi。


尋找 IP 位址 

開啟命令提示字元。輸入 ipconfig，然後按 enter 鍵。尋找根據您為您的路由器的 IP 位址的網路介面卡的預設閘道。尋找 "IPv4 Address" 相同的配接器部分，以查找您的電腦的 IP 位址下。

如何從 Android 上存取共用的 Windows 資料夾 (SMB)


啟用檔案共用

開啟「控制台」，按一下選擇 [網路和網際網路] 選項下的 [選擇家用群組和共用選項]，然後按一下 [變更進階共用設定]，再點選 [啟用檔案和印表機共用] 的功能。


附加檔案共用設定

您還可以在此處配置其他進階共用設定。 
 例如，如果您信任本地網路上的所有裝置，您可以啟用對沒有密碼的檔案進行存取。 [啟用檔案和印表機共用] 之後，您可以開啟「檔案資源管理員」或「Windows 檔案總管」，按下右鍵您想要共用的資料夾並選擇 [屬性]。 
 按一下 [共用] 按鈕，使此資料夾可在網路上使用。


請確保兩個裝置都在相同的 Wi-Fi 上

此功能使檔案可在本機網路上使用，因此您的 PC 和行動裝置必須在同一本地網路上。您無法透過網際網路存取共用的 Windows 資料夾，或者當智慧手機連線至行動數據時 — — 也必須連線至 Wi-Fi。


尋找 IP 位址

開啟「命令提示字元」。輸入「ipconfig」，然後按 [Enter] 鍵。尋找根據您為您的路由器的 IP 位址的網路介面卡的預設閘道。尋找「\"IPv4 Address\" 」同一款配接器以尋找您的電腦的 IP 位址。


在 smb 對話方塊中輸入詳細資訊
